## Dependencies
node_modules/
.pnp/
.pnp.*
.yarn/

## Build output
dist/
build/
*.tsbuildinfo

## Studio client bundles MUST ship in the marketplace tarball; the blanket
## `dist/` rule above would silently exclude them, which is exactly the
## v0.6.0–v0.8.2 packaging bug that motivated this exception. Temporary
## measure until the source-shipped re-architecture (Phase 1+4 of
## docs/source-shipped-deskwork-plan/) retires the dist/ directory in
## favor of runtime esbuild. The release workflow's bundle-verification
## step covers this path explicitly to catch any drift.
!plugins/deskwork-studio/public/dist/
!plugins/deskwork-studio/public/dist/**

## Phase 23e runtime build cache. The studio esbuilds client modules
## from public/src/ into <pluginRoot>/.runtime-cache/dist/ at boot.
## Never committed; populated on first run, reused on warm boots.
plugins/deskwork-studio/.runtime-cache/

